                "text": "Any devs interested in tinkering on a tool to export social graph/network data from walled gardens like LinkedIn/Facebook/Discord, and build some lo-fi chat/comms on top?\n\nI've been hacking on this starting with LinkedIn.  If you enable authentication with LinkedIn's 3-legged flow ("
              },
